        "creation_date": 1361374958,
        "body": "<p>Found it. <\/p>\n\n<p>TelephonyManager seem to only work for incoming calls.<\/p>\n\n<p>For outgoing calls create a broadcast listener with an intent android.intent.action.NEW_OUTGOING_CALL string parametrer for the IntentFilter and don't forget to give permission in AndroidMenifest to PROCESS_OUTGOING_CALLS. This will work. Whenever there is an outgoing call the onReceive will be called in the broadcast listener.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 14983952,
        "question_id": 14983759
    }],
